he subscriber\u2019s death, while receiving pension the spouse of SMF beneficiary would receive 50% of pension received by beneficiary as family pension. For this, he / she must not already be an SMF beneficiary of the PM Kisan Pension Scheme.", "007-normal": "In case the death of the subscriber happens during the period of contribution, then spouse shall have the option of continuing the scheme by paying regular contribution or terminating it."}, "004-section": {"000-title": "Synergy b/w PM Farmer Pension Scheme & PM Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana", "001-normal": "There would be complete synergy between PM Farmer Pension Scheme & PM Kisan Nidhi Yojana. The striking feature is that the farmers can opt to allow his / her monthly contribution to the PM Farmer Pension Scheme to be made from the benefits drawn from Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi (PM-KISAN) scheme directly.", "002-normal": "As an alternate method, a farmer can pay his monthly contribution by registering through Common Service Centres (CSCs) under MeitY."}, "005-section": {"000-title": "PM Kisan Pension Scheme Approval", "001-normal": "For the past 70 years after independence, such a coverage for farmers was never thought. In the run up to the Lok Sabha Elections 2019, PM Narendra Modi has mooted this idea to find resonance across the length and breadth of India. After the huge win in the LS elections and after taking oath, PM in his 1st cabinet meeting has approved the PM Farmers Pension Scheme."}, "006-section": {"000-title": "Modi 2.0 1st Cabinet Decisions", "001-normal": "\u2014 [PM Modi Pension Scheme for Retail Traders & Shopkeepers](https://sarkariyojana.com/pm-modi-pension-scheme-retail-traders-small-shopkeepers/)  \n \u2014 [PM Scholarship Scheme Assistance Hiked](https://sarkariyojana.com/pm-scholarship-scheme-pmss-assistance-hiked-boys-girls/)  \n \u2014 [PM Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana Extended](https://sarkariyojana.com/pm-kisan-samman-nidhi-yojana-new-beneficiary-list/)", "002-normal": "Source / 